                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#61r">Fol. 61r</locus>: Record concerning the sale of the book.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 61r: ዕለት፡ 21፡ 3/ 1999 ዓ፡ ካብ፡ ቐሽ፡ ገ/ኪሮስ፡ ይሳቅ፡ ወረዳ፡ ዳጐዓ፡ ተምቤን፡ ቍሸት፡ ቀቀማ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ድርሳነ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም፡ ብ350፡ ቀርሺ፡ ሸይጠ፡ አለኩ፡ ንአባተስፋ፡ ሚካኤል፡ አርአያ፡ ብምሻጠይ፡ ብፍርማይ ቀሺ ገ/ኪሮስ </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">On the day 21 Ṭǝqǝmt 1999 year [of mercy] from priest Gäbrä Kiros Yǝsaq, wäräda Dagwäʿa Tämben, qušät Qäqäma, I sold the book “Homily on the Saviour of the World” for 350 bǝrr to ʾabba Täsfa Mikaʾel ʾArʾaya, by my selling, by my signature [Signature:] priest Gäbrä Kiros</q>
                           The recent note is written in Tǝgrǝñña, in pen. It mentions the day of the transaction, 21 Ṭǝqǝmt 1999 year of mercy (= 30 November 2006 A.D.), the seller and most probably the scribe, priest Gäbrä Kiros Yǝsḥaq from wäräda Dägʿa Tämben, qušät Qäqäma, the buyer ʾabba Täsfa Mikaʾel ʾArʾaya and the sum paid, 350 bǝrr.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Lacunas in supplication formulas for writing a donor’s name are most often not filled. &#xD;
- Donor’s names are crudely written in a blue pen, probably by the same hand as Additio 1.</item>
                     </list>
